These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, december, july, march, september, february, may
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, biathlon, cycling, rugby, surfing, tennis
 1. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 5. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
14. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
16. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
18. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
19. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking tea##1
20. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | tea        | 7up       | lemonade | milk     |
| Birthday   | february   | may       | july  | november  | march  | december   | september  |
| Sport         | tennis | rugby         | surfing  | basketball | badminton | cycling  | biathlon |

