 8. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the owner of the frog is the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person who likes white is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
14. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
15. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
17. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
18. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes purple##1
19. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes black##1
